          <strong id="Introduction">Introduction</strong>

          <p>The Virginia Society of Certified Public Accountants (“VSCPA”) respects the personal information of its
            membership and visitors of the <a href="http://www.vscpa.com">www.VSCPA.com</a> website (“Website”). The
            VSCPA makes every effort to protect such information and use it responsibly and appropriately. This privacy
            policy explains how the VSCPA collects and processes your Personal Data. Each time you use our Website, the
            current version of this policy will apply.</p>

          <p>“Personal Data” is any information that enables us to identify you, directly or indirectly, by reference to
            an identifier such as your name, identification number, location data, online identifier or one or more
            factors specific to your physical, physiological, genetic, mental, economic, cultural or social
            identity.</p>

